      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an accessible entry point. It shows its age cosmetically, but delivers solid value for buyers seeking an inexpensive daily driver, backup vehicle, or project opportunity. A practical choice for someone who wants dependable utility without a big upfront cost.",
