    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Clean title and priced to move, this is a solid budget-friendly car for someone who needs simple, dependable transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it starts, runs, and gets the job done. Great option for a commuter, first-time driver, or anyone looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right owner. If you want honest value and a car that can still serve well, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with a durable powertrain, clean-shifting transmission, and dependable road manners. This is a budget-friendly driver that shows its age cosmetically, but it still delivers honest mechanical performance and has clearly been kept in service rather than neglected. Ideal for someone who wants affordable transportation, a project platform, or a practical spare vehicle with good bones. Priced to move for the right buyer who appreciates value.",
      "price": 5950.0,
