      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Rough around the edges, priced to sell. Honest poor-condition car with solid value for a cheap daily, project, or parts. First serious buyer gets it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with unmistakable presence, this car has the kind of honest character you can\u2019t fake. It turns heads with its classic lines and carries the sort of lived-in story that makes a weekend project feel exciting instead of ordinary. Perfect for someone who sees potential where others see a blank canvas, it\u2019s an ideal candidate for a creative revival, parts use, or a budget-friendly entry into ownership with personality. If you\u2019ve been looking for something with soul, possibility, and room to make it your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 7450.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Dependable, affordable transportation with real value for the budget-conscious buyer. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains a practical option for someone seeking low-cost motoring, a backup car, or a project with potential. Offered with straightforward presentation and priced to reflect its condition while still delivering solid everyday utility.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect and is being sold in poor condition, but it\u2019s an affordable option for someone handy or anyone who needs basic transportation on a budget. Great candidate for a fixer-upper, parts car, or a simple runaround if you\u2019re willing to give it some TLC. Priced to move and worth a look for the right buyer.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid mechanical bones and plenty of upside for the next owner. The engine fires up, pulls cleanly, and the drivetrain feels like it still has good life in it. Suspension, chassis, and major components offer a workable foundation for a budget commuter, shop truck, or light project. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but this is the kind of vehicle buyers look for when they want something straightforward, serviceable, and worth putting a little effort into. Priced to reflect condition while still highlighting the value in a usable, capable platform.",
